540
00:33:54,956 --> 00:33:57,268
Why don't you go somewhere else
to find what you want?

541
00:33:57,348 --> 00:33:58,820
Stop having this idea again, okay?

542
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:00,428
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

