It's a tree connected by root.

574
00:36:24,690 --> 00:36:26,665
This piece is the south part.

575
00:36:27,127 --> 00:36:28,426
This piece is the east.

576
00:36:28,506 --> 00:36:30,053
All deviated from the main root.

577
00:36:31,094 --> 00:36:34,049
Same but different.

578
00:36:38,348 --> 00:36:40,331
But is this in line with our theme?

579
00:36:40,411 --> 00:36:42,539
You can even see that?

580
00:36:43,112 --> 00:36:45,270
This son of President Ren,

581
00:36:45,735 --> 00:36:47,558
