590
00:37:16,529 --> 00:37:19,747
About 10 years or so.

591
00:37:20,963 --> 00:37:22,239
Then how long do you think...

592
00:37:22,319 --> 00:37:24,384
they were together
when they were still trees?

593
00:37:25,417 --> 00:37:28,327
About 360 years.

594
00:37:29,503 --> 00:37:31,385
Just 360 years?

595
00:37:31,851 --> 00:37:35,934
But I want to be with you forever.

596
00:37:37,541 --> 00:37:40,393
I want to be with you forever too.
